00:22:25.090 --> 00:22:28.450 align:middle line:10%
with body weights greater
than 25 to 50 kilograms.

00:22:28.450 --> 00:22:31.150 align:middle line:10%
But small animals
were also affected.

00:22:31.150 --> 00:22:33.670 align:middle line:10%
North America was the most
strongly affected area,

00:22:33.670 --> 00:22:36.700 align:middle line:10%
but the events also
