>>JAYE: Oh, no, bigger.

00:48:17.660 --> 00:48:18.460 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: Bigger?

00:48:18.460 --> 00:48:19.610 align:middle line:10%
>>JAYE: Oh, yes.

