>>JAYE: Or froze.

00:49:20.780 --> 00:49:21.080 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yeah.

00:49:21.080 --> 00:49:21.880 align:middle line:90%
>>JAYE: Or froze.

00:49:21.880 --> 00:49:22.940 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Or froze.

00:49:22.940 --> 00:49:24.606 align:middle line:10%
>>JAYE: But what's
interesting though is

