There was no need to go north.

00:49:44.716 --> 00:49:45.591 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: No need, OK.

00:49:45.591 --> 00:49:48.607 align:middle line:84%
>>JAYE: Because they were living
in an idyllic environment.

00:49:48.607 --> 00:49:49.940 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Do you know Frank Hoff?

